  • Constructor Details

    • Vehicle

      public Vehicle(String brand, String model, int year, double hourlyRentalCost, double dailyRentalCost)
      Constructs a new Bike object with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      brand - The brand of the bike.
      model - The model of the bike.
      year - The manufacturing year of the bike.
      hourlyRentalCost - The hourly rental cost of the bike.
      dailyRentalCost - The daily rental cost of the bike.
      bikeType - The type of the bike (Mountain, Road, Hybrid, etc.).
      fuelLevel - The fuel level of the bike.
